Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.41,0:44:13.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.22,0:44:16.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我们迎来了生死离别
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.02,0:44:20.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.07,0:44:25.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,侦探 已经死了
